name: Free-living marine nematodes from the Southern Bight of the North Sea
description: The nematode communities from 102 stationsin the SouthernBight of the North Sea,sampled between 1972and 1984, are examined. On thewhole, 456 species, belonging to 159 genera and 37 families were found.
